      <body>
         <div type="edition"
              ana="#b1"
              subtype="diplomatic"
              xml:id="hamm0057.diplomatic"
              corresp="#hamm0057.transcription #hamm0057.translation">
            <p>ΕΠΕΙΦΛSΠΕΤΡΟΥΡΩΜΑΝΟΥ<lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ΟΥΤΟΥΜΕΓΑΛΟΠΡ,Ε<lb/>
ΚΑΙΕΥΔΟΚΙΜΟΤΑΤΟΥΗΜΩΝΑΡΧΟΝΤS<lb/>
ΚΑΙΤΟΥΤΟΤΟΕΡΓΟΝΕΓΕΝΕΤΟS
</p>
         </div>
         <div type="edition"
              ana="#b1"
              subtype="transcription"
              xml:id="hamm0057.transcription"
              corresp="#hamm0057.diplomatic #hamm0057.translation">
            <p>Ἐπ<surplus>ε</surplus>ὶ <expan><abbr>Φλ</abbr><ex>αουίου</ex></expan> Πέτρου Ῥωμανοῦ<lb/>
               <supplied reason="undefined">φιλοχρίστ</supplied>ου τοῦ
                     <expan><abbr>μεγαλοπρε</abbr><ex>πεστάτου</ex></expan>
               <lb/> καὶ εὐδοκιμοτάτου ἡμῶν <expan><abbr>ἄρχοντ</abbr><ex>ος</ex></expan>
               <lb/> καὶ τοῦτο τὸ ἔργον ἐγένετο <surplus>Ϛ</surplus>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="hamm0057.translation"
              corresp="#hamm0057.diplomatic #hamm0057.transcription">
            <p>In the time of [Christ-loving] <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#hamm0057p01">Flavius Petrus Romanus</persName>, our most magnificent and glorious <rs type="admTitle">governor</rs>, also this work was done.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The inscription commemorates the building, or rather the rebuilding or restoration of the oval pool next to the hot spring</p>
         </div>
